1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses the deployment of DNNs for various AI applications, including image and video processing, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper focuses on the deployment of DNNs, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper discusses the optimised mapping of DNNs on embedded platforms, which involves designing hardware architectures for efficient deployment. 
4. cs.EM (Embedded Systems) - The paper specifically focuses on the deployment of DNNs on embedded systems, which falls under the domain of embedded systems. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the deployment of DNNs on mobile and embedded systems, which involves designing control systems for efficient deployment.
